{{zh-hanzi|[[一]][[家]][[大小]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: One house, big and small.

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' yī jiā dàxiǎo)
# the whole family
#: ''[[放假]][[了]][[我们]]'''一家大小'''[[往]][[乡下]][[去]][[探望]][[祖母]]。 ([[Simplified Chinese|simplified]])
#: ''[[放假]][[了]]，[[我們]]'''一家大小'''[[往]][[鄉下]][[去]][[探望]][[祖母]]。'' ([[Traditional Chinese|traditional]])
#: ''We had a holiday, so our '''whole family''' went to the countryside to visit grandmother.''

